{"tid":2006751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如由今日開始每日關心上庭手足既狀況呀","createTime":"2020-05-08T03:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T06:24:09.000Z","uid":78892,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe588b970bab318fbdc1a89351d077389715ed2","tid":2006751,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上想同咁多位未做過旁聽師既人介紹一個tg台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(法庭文字直播台),channel admin會實時直播法庭審訊進度同判刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0Lc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=638da218\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live</a><br />\n今朝已經有兩位手足判左八個月同一位手足判入勞教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,希望大家唔好忘記佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做唔到旁聽師都仲有方法關心被捕被判監手足,大家唔好當冇左件事,唔好令手足覺得自己係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b21b332fe4d6eb904210cbabcf2379f935d9785","tid":2006751,"uid":144105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"12eed6d8b73bd98b71b40c16dc4fa57bd5acf5bb","tid":2006751,"uid":78892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"判詞如下:<br />\n當晚有人集結示威，附近被警員發現，並搜出所列違禁武器，即使沒有使用，但要明白對公眾潛在一定安全風險。<br />\n判刑<br />\nD1（26）<br />\n持有伸縮警棍<br />\n袋內被搜出1支鐳射筆<br />\n<br />\nD2（24）<br />\n袋內被搜出丫差，以及數十粒鋼珠<br />\n<br />\nD1,2<br />\n各自在蘇文隆席前承認控罪<br />\n量刑起點：12個月<br />\n認罪扣減3分1<br />\n二人即時監禁8個月<br />\n<br />\nD3（19）<br />\n由於年紀較輕，判入勞教所<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e77fb2ff323926a921b38c0ad26bddc9da21be","tid":2006751,"uid":78892,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"有影到手足被捕前後既片可以send比呢個台,佢地有時會幫手足搵片做証供<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_evidence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_evidence&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0Lc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=8eff9c2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_evidence</a>"},{"pid":"9d5ea2441afcd11dc142891625eabcee777b85ee","tid":2006751,"uid":334646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:01:32.000Z","msg":"認同。琴日101義士上庭得唔夠50人聲援，明明半年前102有成千人去西九法院聲援101義士。<br />\n明明而家大專唔洗番學，點解願意出黎聲援嘅人咁少? 真係當義士係手足就關心多啲，屋企人朋友上庭你都會空個schedule去陪佢地。"},{"pid":"4c44690c0569e28bf1269e597dd9f03576c9bf6e","tid":2006751,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"係咪聲援左佢地就唔洗坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568a94f8381da2aa962487b0ba83ae699d8a1161","tid":2006751,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62b98b339b6cac8bf77109272a557b4ea7acc5b","tid":2006751,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d5ea2441afcd11dc142891625eabcee777b85ee","tid":2006751,"uid":334646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:01:32.000Z","msg":"認同。琴日101義士上庭得唔夠50人聲援，明明半年前102有成千人去西九法院聲援101義士。<br />\n明明而家大專唔洗番學，點解願意出黎聲援嘅人咁少? 真係當義士係手足就關心多啲，屋企人朋友上庭你都會空個schedule去陪佢地。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:03:22.000Z","msg":"要提升番大家士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c00f951302aa78b14d6c4369691230458d732b","tid":2006751,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c44690c0569e28bf1269e597dd9f03576c9bf6e","tid":2006751,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:02:30.000Z","